doc_summary_long: French air power on Wednesday killed at least 10 jihadists in northeast Mali near the border with Algeria, local and foreign military sources said. 'French forces on Wednesday led at least one raid near Tinzaouatene, at the Algerian border, against the terrorists,' a local Malian military source told AFP. 'There were at least 10 deaths and two vehicles were destroyed.'
doc_summary_short: French air power on Wednesday killed at least 10 jihadists in northeast Mali near the border with Algeria, local and foreign military sources said.
doc_title: French raid in Mali leaves at least 10 jihadists dead
